cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The mention of the Transformer architecture indicates that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the potential application of the technique to image captioning suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
